#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.18:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Sīhanādavagga"
msgstr "2. The Lion’s Roar"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Navaṅguposathasutta"
msgstr "18. The Sabbath with Nine Factors"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.389"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.18:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Navahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato uposatho upavuttho mahapphalo hoti "
"mahānisaṃso mahājutiko mahāvipphāro."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, the observance of the sabbath with its nine factors is very "
"fruitful and beneficial and splendid and bountiful."

msgctxt "an9.18:1.2"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ upavuttho ca, bhikkhave, navahaṅgehi samannāgato uposatho mahapphalo "
"hoti mahānisaṃso mahājutiko mahāvipphāro?"
msgstr "And how should it be observed?"

msgctxt "an9.18:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple reflects:"

msgctxt "an9.18:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘yāvajīvaṃ arahanto pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā nihitadaṇḍā "
"nihitasatthā lajjī dayāpannā sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampino viharanti;"
msgstr ""
"‘As long as they live the perfected ones give up killing living creatures, "
"renouncing the rod and the sword. They are scrupulous and kind, and live "
"full of compassion for all living beings."

msgctxt "an9.18:1.5"
msgid ""
"ahampajja imañca rattiṃ imañca divasaṃ pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā "
"paṭivirato nihitadaṇḍo nihitasattho lajjī dayāpanno "
"sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī viharāmi."
msgstr ""
"I, too, for this day and night will give up killing living creatures, "
"renouncing the rod and the sword. I’ll be scrupulous and kind, and live full "
"of compassion for all living beings."

#. VAR: Imināpaṅgena → imināpi aṅgena (si)
msgctxt "an9.18:1.6"
msgid ""
"Imināpaṅgena arahataṃ anukaromi; uposatho ca me upavuttho bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"I will observe the sabbath by doing as the perfected ones do in this "
"respect.’"

msgctxt "an9.18:1.7"
msgid "Iminā paṭhamena aṅgena samannāgato hoti … pe …. (1–7.)"
msgstr "This is its first factor. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.390"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.18:2.1"
msgid ""
"‘Yāvajīvaṃ arahanto uccāsayanamahāsayanaṃ pahāya uccāsayanamahāsayanā "
"paṭiviratā nīcaseyyaṃ kappenti—mañcake vā tiṇasanthārake vā;"
msgstr ""
"‘As long as they live the perfected ones give up high and luxurious beds. "
"They sleep in a low place, either a small bed or a straw mat."

msgctxt "an9.18:2.2"
msgid ""
"ahampajja imañca rattiṃ imañca divasaṃ uccāsayanamahāsayanaṃ pahāya "
"uccāsayanamahāsayanā paṭivirato nīcaseyyaṃ kappemi—mañcake vā tiṇasanthārake "
"vā."
msgstr ""
"I, too, for this day and night will give up high and luxurious beds. I’ll "
"sleep in a low place, either a small bed or a straw mat."

msgctxt "an9.18:2.3"
msgid ""
"Imināpaṅgena arahataṃ anukaromi; uposatho ca me upavuttho bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"I will observe the sabbath by doing as the perfected ones do in this "
"respect.’"

msgctxt "an9.18:2.4"
msgid "Iminā aṭṭhamena aṅgena samannāgato hoti. (8)"
msgstr "This is its eighth factor."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: abyāpajjena → abyāpajjhena (bj, s1-3, mr) | avyāpajjhena (pts1) | abyābajjhena (?)
msgctxt "an9.18:3.1"
msgid ""
"Mettāsahagatena cetasā ekaṃ disaṃ pharitvā viharati, tathā dutiyaṃ tathā "
"tatiyaṃ tathā catutthaṃ. Iti uddhamadho tiriyaṃ sabbadhi sabbattatāya "
"sabbāvantaṃ lokaṃ mettāsahagatena cetasā vipulena mahaggatena appamāṇena "
"averena abyāpajjena pharitvā viharati."
msgstr ""
"They meditate spreading a heart full of love to one direction, and to the "
"second, and to the third, and to the fourth. In the same way above, below, "
"across, everywhere, all around, they spread a heart full of love to the "
"whole world—abundant, expansive, limitless, free of enmity and ill will."

msgctxt "an9.18:3.2"
msgid "Iminā navamena aṅgena samannāgato hoti. (9)"
msgstr "This is its ninth factor."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an9.18:4.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ upavuttho kho, bhikkhave, navahaṅgehi samannāgato uposatho mahapphalo "
"hoti mahānisaṃso mahājutiko mahāvipphāro”ti."
msgstr ""
"The observance of the sabbath with its nine factors in this way is very "
"fruitful and beneficial and splendid and bountiful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.18:4.2"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
